---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import ArchitectureDiagram from '../components/ArchitectureDiagram.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Governed AI Platform and Agents for Insurance | NorthLine Consulting';
const pageDescription =
	'A governed AI platform approach for insurers and MGUs adopting agentic process automation in regulated environments.';
---

<MainLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
	<section class="section architecture-page-intro">
		<div class="section-heading">
			<p class="eyebrow">AI Platform</p>
			<h1>Governed AI Platform and Agents for Insurance</h1>
		</div>

		<p class="architecture-page-copy">
			You know AI can help reduce workload across underwriting, claims, and operations, but it
			must meet IT, cyber, and compliance requirements. IT teams want to support adoption, but
			are already stretched and often lack hands-on experience implementing AI platforms at scale.
		</p>

		<p class="architecture-page-copy architecture-page-copy-emphasis">
			Developers can build solutions, but establishing effective, repeatable design patterns takes
			time, cost, and carries real risk in regulated environments.
		</p>

		<p class="architecture-page-copy">
			NorthLine implements a governed AI platform aligned to Microsoft Agent 365 architecture
			patterns and enterprise best practices, bringing control, security, and structure to AI
			adoption. We deliver Agentic AI accelerators that can be rapidly fine-tuned to your data,
			workflows, and operating model.
		</p>

		<ArchitectureDiagram />

		<p class="architecture-page-copy architecture-page-copy-emphasis">
			AI is not the center. Control is the center. Platform before agents. That is what allows
			insurers, MGUs, delegated authority businesses, and partner-led operating models to adopt AI
			without losing control of risk, compliance, or execution.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section class="section contact-section architecture-contact-section">
		<p class="eyebrow">You&apos;ve moved beyond pilots. Now make it real.</p>
		<div class="contact-card">
			<div>
				<p class="eyebrow">Get Started</p>
				<h2>Bring your AI platform into production, under governance.</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="contact-content">
				<p>
					NorthLine works with business, IT, and compliance teams to implement governed AI
					platforms and deploy purpose-built agents in regulated insurance environments.
				</p>
				<button class="button button-primary" type="button" data-open-contact>
					Start a Conversation
				</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<dialog class="contact-modal" id="contact-modal">
		<form class="contact-modal-card" id="contact-form" method="dialog" novalidate>
			<div class="contact-modal-header">
				<div>
					<p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
					<h2>Start a Conversation</h2>
				</div>
				<button class="contact-modal-close" type="button" aria-label="Close form" data-close-contact>
					<span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
				</button>
			</div>

			<div class="contact-form-grid">
				<label class="field">
					<span>Name</span>
					<input id="contact-name" name="name" type="text" autocomplete="name" required />
				</label>

				<label class="field">
					<span>Email</span>
					<input id="contact-email" name="email" type="email" autocomplete="email" required />
				</label>

				<label class="field">
					<span>Company</span>
					<input id="contact-company" name="company" type="text" autocomplete="organization" required />
				</label>

				<label class="field field-full">
					<span>Message</span>
					<textarea
						id="contact-message"
						name="message"
						rows="5"
						required
						placeholder="Briefly describe the problem, line, or initiative."
					></textarea>
				</label>
			</div>

			<p class="form-status" id="contact-status" aria-live="polite"></p>

			<div class="contact-modal-actions">
				<button class="button button-secondary" type="button" data-close-contact>Cancel</button>
				<button class="button button-primary" type="submit" id="contact-submit">
					Send Inquiry
				</button>
			</div>
		</form>
	</dialog>
</MainLayout>

<script type="module" src="/scripts/contact-form.js"></script>
